                                    <p class="mb-4 ">The Turkish passport is a powerful travel document that ranks 37th in the world in terms of travel freedom, according to the 2023 Visa Guide Passport statistics. This means that it provides its holder with an overall average degree of mobility. It offers a range of advantages to its holders, including:
                                    </p>
