                                    <p class="mb-5 lg:mb-16">The applicant can obtain the advantages of obtaining a Turkish passport within a period not exceeding 6-7 months to obtain a Turkish passport. This decision has undergone many amendments that included real estate investment. Initially, the minimum real estate investment was set at $1,000,000, but the Turkish government later reduced it to $250,000 in 2019. Then in April 2022, it issued a decision to raise the minimum value of real estate investment to $400,000.</p>
                                    <p class="mb-5 lg:mb-16">There are many conditions that must be met in this case of real estate investment, including:</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
